FBIS4-23374 "drafr108_a_94003" FBIS-AFR-94-108 Daily Report 4 Jun 1994 CENTRAL AFRICA Rwanda RPF Attack on Gitarama Reportedly Repulsed RPF Attack on Gitarama Reportedly Repulsed EA0406125594 Kampala Radio Uganda Network in English 1000 GMT 4 Jun 94 EA0406125594 Kampala Radio Uganda Network English BFN [Text] We have just received a report to the effect that the Rwandese Government says its forces have pushed back rebel RPF [Rwandan Patriotic Front] forces, who launched an attack on the town of Gitarama yesterday, after overrunning the nearby town of Kabgayi. Gitarama is reported to be heavily fortified, and observers say any assault on it will not be an easy task.
